** Recursion-to-iteration test 1: Factorial method, non-tail-recursive
public int fact(int n) {
    if (n < 2) {
        return 1;
    }
    return n * fact(n - 1);
}
** Recursion-to-iteration test 2: Factorial method, tail-recursive
public int fact(int n, int acc) {
    if (n < 2) {
        return acc;
    }
    return fact(n - 1, n * acc);
}
